org.chronos.chronograph.api.builder.query

Interface GraphWhereBuilder<E extends org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Element>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - Either Vertex or Edge, depending on the result type of this query.

    public interface GraphWhereBuilder<E extends org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Element>
    A step in the fluent graph query builder API. Specifies the details of a filer operation.
